# `.github/copilot-instructions.md` Template

## Purpose

Provide concise repository instructions for GitHub Copilot.

## Core Rules

- `AGENT.md` is canonical.
- Follow DDD/Hex architecture boundaries.
- Keep controllers thin and use-case driven.
- Avoid cross-context coupling outside approved patterns.

## Quality Requirements

- Add/update tests for behavior changes.
- Provide clear PR evidence for generated changes.
- Document assumptions and residual risks.

## Escalation

Stop and request human decision for high-risk security/data-integrity ambiguities.
